 family of Muhammad, O’ Lord of Muhammad protect the absence of Muhammad, O’ Lord of Muhammad retaliate for the daughter of Muhammad (peace be on them).", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Muhammad (s.a.w.a) ke Rab! Aale Muhammad (a.s) ke zahoor me taajil (jaldi) farma, Ay Muhammad (s.a.w.a) ke Rab! Muhammad (Mahdi a.s) ki ghaibat ki hifaazat farma, Ay Muhammad (s.a.w.a) ke Rab! Muhammad (s.a.w.a) ki dukhtar (beti) ka intekaam le. Allah ka durood o salaam ho un par aur unki Aal par.", "Urdu": "اے محمدؐ کے رب! آل محمدؑ کے ظہور میں جلدی فرما، اے محمدؐ کے رب! محمد (مہدیؑ) کی غیبت کی حفاظت فرما، اے محمدؐ کے رب! محمدؐ کی بیٹی کا انتقام لے، اللہ کا درود و سلام ہو ان پر اور ان کی آل پر۔", "RArabic": "YAA RABBA MOHAMMADIN A’JJIL FARA-JA AALE MOHAMMADIN, YAA RABBA MOHAMMADIN EH-FAZ GHAIBA-TA MOHAMMADIN, YAA RABBA MOHAMMADIN INTE-QIM LIBNA-TE MOHAMMADIN A’LAIYHE-MAS SALAAMO.", "ArabicText1": "یَا رَبَّ مُحَمَّدٍ عَجِّلْ فَرَجَ آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ، یَا رَبَّ مُحَمَّدٍ اِحْفَظْ غَیْبَۃَ مُحَمَّدٍ، یَا رَبَّ مُحَمَّدٍ اِنْتَقِمْ لِابْنَۃِ مُحَمَّدٍ عَلَیْهِمَا السَّلَامُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": n